txt.en: While battling against the forces in Tarlang's Crown, you have encountered the Umbarrim. These hale Men seemingly possess Black Númenórean-blood, and stand taller than the other Corsairs that serve under Azruthor.\n\nUnless they are defeated, such strength could be devastating to the people of Gondor.
You have defeated many Umbarrim in Tarlang's Crown.
The Umbarrim in Tarlang's Crown enjoy the strength of the Black Númenóreans, a line long-assumed to have vanished from Middle-earth.
The Umbarrim can be found throughout Tarlang's Crown, especially in the central camp.\n\nYou have encountered the Umbarrim and should defeat them, lest their might be used against Gondor.
You have defeated many of the Umbarrim in Tarlang's Crown. While not all of their number have been slain, you have slowed their advance into the Anfalas and protected the lands surrounding the Crown.
